{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-posts-js","path":"/posts/조엘온소프트웨어다시읽기","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>2005년에 출판된 책이다. 현재 사정과 많이 다를 수도 있다.</h1>\n<h1>2장 Back to the Basic, 기본으로 돌아가기</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://egloos.zum.com/entireboy/v/2767590\">페인트 공 알고리즘</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>ASCIZ 문자열</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>문자열 끝을 Z = 0 로 표시하는 문자열</li>\n<li>n^2 효율</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div id=\"gist88699613\" class=\"gist\">\n    <div class=\"gist-file\">\n      <div class=\"gist-data\">\n        <div class=\"js-gist-file-update-container js-task-list-container file-box\">\n  <div id=\"file-asciz-c\" class=\"file my-2\">\n    \n\n  <div itemprop=\"text\" class=\"Box-body p-0 blob-wrapper data type-c  \">\n      \n<table class=\"highlight tab-size js-file-line-container\" data-tab-size=\"8\" data-paste-markdown-skip>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-L1\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"1\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-LC1\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">void</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">strcat</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">char</span>* dest, <span class=\"pl-k\">char</span>* src)</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-L2\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"2\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-LC2\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">{</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-L3\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"3\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-LC3\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-k\">while</span> (*dest) dest++;</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-L4\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"4\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-asciz-c-LC4\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-k\">while</span> (*dest++ = *src++);</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-asc